profile_summary: As a B-Tech Electronics and Communication student at Cochin University of Science and Technology, I've developed a strong foundation in programming languages such as Rust, Python, and C. With a passion for contributing to FOSS projects, I'm actively learning and growing as a developer. My experience with front-end frameworks like Next JS, React, and Bootstrap, along with backend frameworks like Django and Flask, has equipped me with a versatile skill set. I'm also proficient in cloud computing platforms like AWS, Heroku, and Firebase, and have experience with databases like SQLite and Postgres. When I'm not coding, you can find me on Instagram or LinkedIn, or exploring new design tools like Adobe Lightroom and Figma. With over 54 public repositories and 26 followers, I'm committed to sharing my knowledge and collaborating with like-minded developers.
